		<title>贝莱德提交ETF申请，以太币大涨</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/market-news/ethereum-surge-blackrock-etf-filing</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
